1
00:00:07,879 --> 00:00:09,033
You see? These are too small.
你看到了吗? 这些太小了.

2
00:00:09,931 --> 00:00:10,604
How big do you want them?
你想要多大的?

3
00:00:11,125 --> 00:00:12,538
Twelve inches by eighteen inches.
12英寸×18英寸.

4
00:00:12,991 --> 00:00:15,444
Twelve by eighteen. Fine.
12×18. 好的.

5
00:00:16,610 --> 00:00:18,963
And not this thin material. It doesn't last.
还有,不要这种薄面料. 很不耐用.

6
00:00:19,233 --> 00:00:20,082
I want thicker cloth.
我要厚一点的.

7
00:00:21,144 --> 00:00:21,507
What about...
那...

8
00:00:22,056 --> 00:00:24,044
And just plain white. No fancy designs.
只要素白色. 不要有花哨的图案.

9
00:00:24,810 --> 00:00:25,042
OK.
OK.

10
00:00:25,971 --> 00:00:26,973
And finished edges.
还有, 锁好边.

11
00:00:27,590 --> 00:00:28,406
Would you like anything else?
你还要点别的吗?

12
00:00:29,541 --> 00:00:32,008
Yes. I want a shipment of guest towels.
是的, 我还想要一批给客人用的毛巾.

13
00:00:33,296 --> 00:00:33,694
200 towels.
200条.

14
00:00:35,062 --> 00:00:36,914
Sixteen inches by thirty inches.
16英寸×30英寸.

15
00:00:38,256 --> 00:00:39,265
100%cotton.
100%纯棉.

16
00:00:40,491 --> 00:00:44,616
In "Warm Cream". With the hotel monogram.
"暖米色", 印上饭店的字母图案(monogram).

17
00:00:45,453 --> 00:00:45,883
If you wish.
如果你想的话.

18
00:00:46,383 --> 00:00:46,816
I do wish.
我确实想.

19
00:00:48,566 --> 00:00:50,856
We have a new line of terrycloth robes.
我们还有一种新款毛巾浴衣(terrycloth robes).

20
00:00:52,348 --> 00:00:52,808
They're lighter.
质地较轻.

21
00:00:53,843 --> 00:00:55,230
Very nice for the hot weather.
非常适合热天用.

22
00:00:55,883 --> 00:00:56,686
Can you send me a sample?
你能给我寄一件样品来吗?

23
00:00:57,359 --> 00:00:57,732
Of course.
当然.

24
00:00:58,095 --> 00:00:58,499
I'll decide then.
然后我再决定.

25
00:00:59,636 --> 00:01:01,698
Always a pleasure doing business with you, NuLa.
和你做生意总是很愉快, NuLa.

26
00:01:02,642 --> 00:01:03,458
Likewise, Vinny.
我也是, Vinny.

27
00:01:05,566 --> 00:01:06,956
I'll call again in two weeks.
两周以后我再打电话.

28
00:01:07,414 --> 00:01:07,716
See you then.
到时再见.

29
00:01:08,166 --> 00:01:08,516
So long!
再见!

30
00:01:08,793 --> 00:01:09,117
Good bye!
再见!

31
00:01:10,464 --> 00:01:11,637
You always get the last word.
你总是说最后一句话.

32
00:01:12,151 --> 00:01:12,539
Yes, I do.
是的.

